==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outname
<hw>Out*name"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
exceed in naming or describing.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To exceed in name, fame, or degree.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And found out one to <qex>outname</qex> thy other faults.</q>
<rj><qau>Beau. & Fl.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outness</ent>⟦br⟧
